                    </div>
                    <span>I was unable to penetrate Gamma et al before reading this book and was able to make use of Gamma et al after reading the book. Reading this book was a major breakthrough in my capacity as an object oriented programmer.<P>Clear and insightful, easy to read yet precise. If you understand the nuts and bolts of an OO language but feel you aren't quite "getting it" this book may very well get you over the hump.<P>Very highly recommended.</span>
                  
              
